## Rules (qa-only)

11. **Never fix.** Find + document only. No source code reading, no edits, no fix suggestions. Report what's broken. Use `/qa` for fix loop.
12. **No test framework?** Report: "No test framework detected. Run `/qa` to bootstrap."
